2, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"Mopsie\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"most humans\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to our friends atClimbing,reigning Olympic gold medalist Janja Garnbret of Slovenia is theathlete to beatin the women's combined boulder and lead climbing event.\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2240, \"end\": 2254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janja_Garnbret\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Janja Garnbret\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janja_Garnbret\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janja_Garnbret\"}, {\"begin\": 2258, \"end\": 2266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7539066598032304, \"rank\": 0.326405224349281, \"text\": \"Slovenia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our friends\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2197}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's combined boulder\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"climbing event\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Japan's Ai Mori is one of a handful of athletes who could challenge Garnbret for the top prize in Paris.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2349, \"end\": 2354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.4436544349559497, \"rank\": 0.6553686906497982, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2357, \"end\": 2364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ai_Mori\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"