rld\", \"from\": 3790, \"to\": 3799}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the years since, he's gone on towin surfing's biggest competitions.\", \"from\": 3801, \"to\": 3871, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 3804, \"to\": 3813}, {\"ngram\": \"towin surfing's biggest competitions\", \"from\": 3834, \"to\": 3870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Florence came in ninth in Tokyo and is going into the Paris Olympic competition-which will be held in Tahiti-at the top of the World Surf League rankings.\", \"from\": 3872, \"to\": 4026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3898, \"end\": 3903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8213207687582855, \"rank\": 0.21755108097687645, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3999, \"end\": 4016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.13972780143793e-21, \"text\": \"World Surf League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Florence\", \"from\": 3872, \"to\": 3880}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympic competition\", \"from\": 3922, \"to\": 3951}, {\"ngram\": \"Tahiti\", \"from\": 3974, \"to\": 3980}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 3984, \"to\": 3991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's hard to put into words exactly what makes Florence such a compelling surfer to watch, especially since I have never surfed in my life, but just watch a minute or two ofthis videoand tell me you are not entertained.\", \"from\": 4027, \"to\": 4246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"words\", \"from\": 4049, \"to\": 4054}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 4055, \"to\": 4067}, {\"ngram